description: 163 W Second street is one of the only 3 family brownstones on the market! A 3family row house that has been converted into condos being sold as a package! Perfect for all kinds investors looking for consistent income in the South Boston market. The building was gutted to studs and renovated in 1988. new hot water boilers & electric heaters, new decks, updated bathrooms. Units have Hardwood floors through out, recess lighting & skylights! Exclusive and highly competitive area close to several T stations/stops, restaurants, and cafe's, and a plethora of other amenities. South Boston has completely transformed over the years due to several high profile industries expanding in the area. Easy access to highways, downtown Boston, Seaport, Castle island and beach. A perfect location for tenants or owner occupancy!
